# Seller Central login (Mahika)

**Account:** `arunsaini416@gmail.com` · **OTP suffix:** `711` · **Telegram:** `@mahika_arun_bot` (6-digit only)  
**Trust device:** always tick — *Don't ask for codes on this device*  
**OTP wait:** **3 attempts × 60s** (Scenario 1)  
**Call 711 (Scenario 2):** submit → **120s** → resubmit → **300s** (×**2** rounds) → fail = log + close  
**Default command:** `python -m mahika.cli seller-login` — cookies **rakho**  
**Full family tree:** `agent/Graphs & workflows/seller-central-login/FLOW.md`

