## Full flow graph (master)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  START([mahika seller-login])

  START --> TST{--fresh flag?}
  TST -->|No — normal| LOAD[Load seller_central_cookies.json]
  TST -->|Yes — test only| CLR[Clear cookies + Chromium profile]
  LOAD --> NAV[Open Seller Central — use saved session]
  CLR --> NAV2[Sign-in URL clean slate]
  NAV --> AUTH{Already home?}
  NAV2 --> S1
  AUTH -->|yes| S6[S6 Home — done]
  AUTH -->|no| PICKACC[Account picker / sign-in if needed]
  PICKACC --> BR
  NAV2 --> S1

  subgraph CRED["Credentials when needed"]
    S1[S1: Email → Continue]
    S1 --> S2[S2: Password → Sign in]
  end

  S2 --> BR{Which screen?}
  PICKACC --> BR

  BR -->|S3| S3PATH[S3: Delivery picker]
  BR -->|S4 already| S4SKIP[S4: OTP entry — skip picker R3]
  BR -->|S5| S5PATH[S5: Didn't receive multi-option]

  subgraph S3FLOW["S3 — Send OTP once"]
    S3PATH --> SC{Scenario}
    SC -->|1 Ideal| DEF[Keep default radio — no WhatsApp re-click]
    SC -->|2 or 3 on picker| CALL711[Select Call …711]
    DEF --> R8A[R8: 60s if radio changed]
    CALL711 --> R8A
    R8A --> SEND[Click Send OTP — 1× only]
    SEND --> R8B[R8: 60s after Send OTP]
    R8B --> RL{Rate limit banner?}
    RL -->|Yes| R8B
    RL -->|No| S4
  end

  S4SKIP --> S4
  S3FLOW --> S4[S4: OTP entry screen]

  subgraph S4FLOW["S4 — OTP + Telegram"]
    S4 --> TRUST[Tick Don't ask codes on this device]
    TRUST --> TG["Telegram wait: 3 × 60s"]
    TG -->|attempt 1/3| T1[Reminder + terminal line]
    T1 --> T2[attempt 2/3]
    T2 --> T3[attempt 3/3]
    T3 -->|OTP received| SUBMIT[Fill OTP → Sign in]
    T3 -->|no OTP| FAIL3[3 min done]
  end

  SUBMIT --> S7[S7: Badeja Enterprises → India → Select account]
  S7 --> S6[S6: Home — save cookies]
  FAIL3 --> S2BUSY[Scenario 2: Call 711 tree]
  S2BUSY --> C1[Submit Call 711]
  C1 --> W120[Wait 120s]
  W120 --> C2[Resubmit Call 711]
  C2 --> W300[Wait 300s + Telegram]
  W300 -->|fail x2| FAIL_CLOSE[Log + script CLOSE]
  W300 -->|OTP| S7

  subgraph SC2["Scenario 2 — Busy"]
    S2BUSY --> DIDNT[S4: Didn't receive OTP?]
    DIDNT --> S5CALL[S5: Call …711 → R8 → Send OTP → R8]
    S5CALL --> S4B[S4 again]
    S4B --> TG2["Telegram 3 × 60s again"]
    TG2 -->|OTP| SUBMIT
    TG2 -->|fail| ENDFAIL([Login failed — otp_failed.png])
  end

  S5PATH --> S5CALL

  subgraph SC3["Scenario 3 — Shortcut"]
    REOPEN([Browser reopen — cookies OK]) --> BR3{S3 or S4?}
    BR3 -->|S3| S3SHORT[Call 711 + Send OTP + R8×2]
    BR3 -->|S4| S4SKIP
    S3SHORT --> S4
  end

  subgraph FORBID["FORBIDDEN"]
    WA[Re-click WhatsApp on S4]
    SPAM[Send OTP twice under 60s]
    WA --> SPAM
  end

  S4 -.->|never| FORBID
```

