## Timing summary

| Phase | Duration |
|-------|----------|
| Each Telegram attempt | 60s |
| Per scenario OTP wait | **3 × 60s = 3 min** |
| Scenario 1 + 2 max OTP wait | up to **6 min** |
| After radio / Send OTP | **+60s each** (R8) |

