## Scenario 1 — Ideal

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Sir
  participant A as Mahika
  participant AM as Amazon
  U->>A: seller-login
  Note over A: Load cookies — no clear
  A->>AM: Account picker or S1/S2
  A->>AM: S3 Send OTP default 1x
  Note over A,AM: R8 wait 60s
  A->>AM: S4 trust device
  loop 3 attempts x 60s
    A->>U: Telegram attempt N/3
    A->>A: Terminal ping
    U-->>A: 6-digit OTP
  end
  A->>AM: Submit OTP
  A->>AM: S7 Badeja → India → Select account
  AM-->>A: S6 Home + cookies
```

