## R8 — Amazon cooldown

After radio select or Send OTP → **60s wait**. RL banner → wait only, no re-click.

---

## R3 — WhatsApp loop (FORBIDDEN)

S4 visible → no picker re-Send. Green WhatsApp banner → 3×60s wait only.

